### Jupyter é—®é¢˜ä¿®å¤
å¦‚æœåœ¨Jupyterä¸­é‡åˆ°ç©ºç™½æ˜¾ç¤ºé—®é¢˜ï¼Œè¿è¡Œä»¥ä¸‹ä»£ç ï¼š

```python
# æ¸…é™¤æ¨¡å—ç¼“å­˜å¹¶é‡æ–°å¯¼å…¥
import sys
for module in list(sys.modules.keys()):
    if module.startswith('g2py'):
        del sys.modules[module]

# é‡æ–°å¯¼å…¥
from g2py import Plot

# åŠ¨æ€æ·»åŠ ç¼ºå¤±çš„æ–¹æ³•ï¼ˆå¦‚æœéœ€è¦ï¼‰
if not hasattr(Plot, 'set_title'):
    def set_title(self, title):
        self.page_title = title
        return self
    Plot.set_title = set_title

if not hasattr(Plot, 'set_options'):
    def set_options(self, options):
        self.options = options
        return self
    Plot.set_options = set_options
```

## ğŸ› ï¸ API å‚è€ƒ

### Plot ç±»

#### æ„é€ å‡½æ•°
